# Design baseline — before full redesign (2026-06-24)

**Git snapshot:** tag `design-baseline/pre-redesign-2026-06` → commit `96637e1`

## Revert commands

```bash
# Full UI rollback to baseline (destructive — stash or branch first)
git checkout design-baseline/pre-redesign-2026-06 -- src/app/globals.css src/app/layout.tsx src/components/ src/lib/utils.ts

# Or browse baseline
git show design-baseline/pre-redesign-2026-06:src/app/globals.css
```

## Visual identity

- **Palette:** Blue/indigo primary (`#2b4dd0`), teal accent (`#0d9488`), slate foreground (`#0f172a`), gray background (`#f9fafb`)
- **Hero gradient:** `#1e3a8a` → `#2b4dd0` → `#14b8a6` (class `.app-hero-surface`)
- **Headline highlight:** `.hero-headline-highlight` — white→blue→green text gradient clip
- **Typography:** Source Sans 3 (400/600/700), base `html { font-size: 18px }`, line-height 1.6
- **Radius:** `--radius: 0.75rem`; buttons/cards use `rounded-xl`
- **Footer:** Dark slate `#0f172a`, muted `#94a3b8`, accent `#60a5fa`

## Layout chrome (order in `layout.tsx`)

`Header` → `TopSessionBanner` → `BreadcrumbBar` → `<main>` → `CrisisBar` (blue `#1e3a8a`) → `Footer`

- **Sticky header:** Compacts on scroll; `--site-header-height` 5rem / compact 3.5rem; smooth `--site-header-offset` transition
- **Crisis bar:** Full-width blue strip, 988 + text line links
- **Library disclaimer:** Light slate bar `#f1f5f9` (full-bleed via `.app-library-disclaimer-bar`) on `/resources` + detail; footer text variant

## Spacing system (`src/lib/utils.ts`)

- `pageSectionPadding`: `px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 sm:py-14 lg:px-8 lg:py-16`
- `resourcesHeroPadding` / `pageHeroPadding` for hero bands
- `sectionStackGap`: `space-y-6`
- **Section bands:** Alternate white (`bg-white`) and muted (`#f9fafb`) via `pageSectionBandClassForIndex`
- **Max widths:** Content `max-w-7xl`, resource detail `max-w-4xl`

## Key components & patterns

| Area | Files |
|------|-------|
| Tokens + utilities | `src/app/globals.css` |
| Header/nav | `src/components/layout/header.tsx`, `header-control-styles.ts`, `header-branding-lockup.tsx` |
| Footer | `src/components/layout/footer.tsx` |
| Hero + search | `src/components/home/hero-section.tsx`, `hero-surface-orbs.tsx` |
| Resource cards | `resource-masonry.tsx`, `resource-card` patterns, `category-badge.tsx` |
| Scroll animations | `src/components/ui/scroll-reveal.tsx` + keyframes in `globals.css` |
| Buttons | `src/components/ui/button.tsx` — variants primary/soft/outline, min-h 44–52px |
| Badges | `.resource-badge`, `.app-badge`, intake signal badge classes in `site-branding-styles.ts` |
| Disclaimer | `src/components/resources/library-disclaimer.tsx` |

## UX conventions (preserve unless redesign explicitly changes)

- Bilingual EN/ES via `useTranslations` / message files — no hardcoded UI strings
- Large touch targets (44px+ buttons), focus rings `outline-3 ring`
- Resources: collapsible location filters, Search applies filters, masonry with stable columns on load-more
- Eligibility cards: yellow tint `--eligibility-bg`
- PDF export layout: `src/lib/pdf/` mirrors web resource detail (compact sidebar cards)

## Do not confuse with redesign work

When implementing a new design, treat this rule as **read-only reference**. Do not merge old tokens into new components unless explicitly reverting.
